  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 8b94c1195cc9272d99a82df3df77782b, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  ArtifactForm: 3
  Names:
  - The Stuff Bamibrosi
  Lines:
  - I'll sue him!
  - Excuse me, it's just that Gladnfis! The sword of light is on yours.
  - He flashed light right at me while my mage was casting DOOM. It almost killed
    me! I'm shocked I made it out alive!
  - 'I''ll take everithyng from him: his mage, his sigil, even his wife! And you''ll
    do all the paperwork!'
